_

32:38.376 --> 32:41.442
_

32:54.159 --> 32:56.643
Ah, I come bearing ribs.

32:56.547 --> 32:59.283
Actually, there's a little
bit of everything, you know,

32:59.317 --> 33:02.185
since we missed the dinner
portion of the awkward dinner.

33:02.220 --> 33:04.488
Right, thank you.

33:04.522 --> 33:07.524
It was really sweet of you.

33:07.558 --> 33:10.227
Your dad told me how
good of an artist you are.

33:10.261 --> 33:12.229
He wasn't kidding.

33:12.263 --> 33:13.597
Thank you.

33:13.631 --> 33:16.199
I could barely draw stick figures.

33:16.234 --> 33:18.335
Hopefully she doesn't inherit

33:18.369 --> 33:20.504
my artistic abilities.

33:20.538 --> 33:23.440
Sorry you got caught up in all this.

33:23.474 --> 33:26.243
I didn't know what to say to that guy.

33:26.277 --> 33:28.445
I hope I didn't get anybody in trouble.

33:28.479 --> 33:30.580
Please. You have enough to worry about.

33:30.615 --> 33:33.250
<i>How's the baby? When's the next checkup?</i>

33:33.284 --> 33:36.153
You can stop competing for
the father of the year award.

33:36.187 --> 33:38.355
She's giving the kid up for adoption.

33:38.389 --> 33:41.591
Why didn't you tell me about this?

33:41.626 --> 33:44.561
Don't you think that's a
decision we both should make?

33:44.595 --> 33:47.297
Why? You weren't a father to Daphne.

33:47.332 --> 33:49.399
You've barely been a father to me.

33:49.434 --> 33:51.401
Why start now?

33:53.137 --> 33:54.304
(Sighs)

33:58.509 --> 34:01.044
This hasn't been easy for us.

34:01.079 --> 34:04.081
Me and Angelo. I mean, we had...

34:04.115 --> 34:06.083
we had really just started to
put the pieces back together

34:06.117 --> 34:08.418
after the whole switched
at birth thing came out.

34:08.453 --> 34:10.454
And then I found out

34:10.487 --> 34:13.255
that Angelo...

34:13.291 --> 34:16.025
my husband had an affair.

34:16.060 --> 34:18.061
When did that happen?

34:18.096 --> 34:19.429
A few months before we were married.

34:19.464 --> 34:22.299
He promised me that it
was a one-time thing...

34:22.333 --> 34:25.202
not that it made it hurt any less.

34:25.235 --> 34:28.170
You're aware that if any of
what you're telling me is false,

34:28.206 --> 34:31.074
you could go to jail.

34:31.029 --> 34:34.331
Yes, but I'm telling you the truth.

34:34.364 --> 34:38.068
I just want you to know that if any
immigration fraud is happening here,

34:38.101 --> 34:40.904
and you tell me about it right now,

34:40.938 --> 34:43.219
I'll make sure no criminal
charges are brought against you.

34:46.217 --> 34:47.985
Now...

34:51.155 --> 34:53.857
Is there anything else
you'd like to tell me?

35:00.765 --> 35:03.066
I'm sorry about what happened with Lana.

35:03.101 --> 35:05.769
I'm not proud of it.

35:05.803 --> 35:07.971
But that has nothing to do with you and me.

35:08.006 --> 35:10.140
Everything everyone has ever told me

35:10.174 --> 35:12.042
about you is true.

35:12.076 --> 35:14.745
What do you want from me?

35:16.080 --> 35:18.849
I wanted

35:18.883 --> 35:21.118
an amazing dad,

35:21.152 --> 35:24.755
like the one that Daphne got when
we first found out about the switch.

35:24.789 --> 35:26.890
And what did I get?

35:28.059 --> 35:29.826
I got a mom who wouldn't
even tell me your name.

35:29.861 --> 35:32.929
That's how badly she
wanted to keep you from me.

35:32.964 --> 35:35.165
But I went looking for you
anyway because I thought

35:35.199 --> 35:37.000
that you would be this...

35:39.037 --> 35:41.204
missing piece that made
everything make sense.

35:41.239 --> 35:45.809
But you are just this huge disappointment.

35:48.112 --> 35:50.814
I gave up my life

35:50.848 --> 35:52.849
in Chicago to come here.

35:52.884 --> 35:55.819
And then I spent four months in detention.

35:55.853 --> 35:58.789
You have no idea what that was like.

35:58.823 --> 36:00.924
I could've gotten out any time I wanted.

36:00.958 --> 36:03.060
All I had to do was to
agree to go back to Italy.

36:05.930 --> 36:07.998
But I stayed so I could be with you.

36:08.032 --> 36:11.968
So if you want to shut me out, it's fine.

36:12.003 --> 36:14.971
But you can never say that I haven't tried.

36:29.982 --> 36:32.917
Based on what Ms. Vasquez just told me,

36:32.952 --> 36:35.220
this marriage has so many
problems, it has to be real.

36:35.254 --> 36:36.221
(Sighs)

36:39.191 --> 36:40.992
We're trying to work through this.

36:41.026 --> 36:44.129
If you can find a way to forgive
Mr. Sorrento his indiscretions,

36:44.163 --> 36:45.830
I guess I can, too.

36:45.865 --> 36:47.198
Thank you.

36:47.233 --> 36:49.901
Well, thank you very much.

36:49.935 --> 36:51.870
Don't forget your baseball. (Chuckles)

36:53.873 --> 36:57.008
Listen, I remember you
two from your interview.

36:57.042 --> 37:00.011
I really hope you can work through
this. You seem like a good couple.

37:04.283 --> 37:06.951
We used to be.

37:08.020 --> 37:09.921
(Sighs)

37:12.124 --> 37:13.191
<i>(Door closes)</i>

37:15.060 --> 37:17.028
<i>- It was nice meeting you again.
- (Car door opens)</i>

37:17.062 --> 37:18.963
<i>- That's it?
- (Car door closes)</i>

37:18.998 --> 37:21.199
<i>- Why didn't you tell me who you were on the elevator?
- (Engine starts)</i>

37:21.233 --> 37:23.868
What were you doing, stalking me?

37:23.903 --> 37:26.237
No, that was an accident.

37:26.272 --> 37:28.840
I just was so...

37:28.874 --> 37:30.074
(Sighs)

37:31.343 --> 37:34.179
I'm sorry. I should've told you.

37:34.213 --> 37:36.881
I just didn't know what to say.

37:39.118 --> 37:41.319
I didn't know about you in Rome.

37:41.353 --> 37:43.354
I don't care.

37:43.389 --> 37:46.024
In fact, I should be thanking you.

37:47.193 --> 37:50.094
It was never gonna work
between me and Angelo.

37:54.099 --> 37:56.000
(Sighs)

37:56.035 --> 37:58.136
I don't know what I was thinking.

37:58.170 --> 37:59.871
I just thought... I don't know...

37:59.905 --> 38:03.208
when I ran into Lana for the
second time totally out of the blue,

38:03.242 --> 38:05.143
I thought it was for a reason.

38:05.177 --> 38:08.046
We had this great connection. I
thought everybody else would, too.

38:08.080 --> 38:10.315
But I don't know.

38:10.349 --> 38:13.184
That's the last time I try
to pull a "Kathryn Kennish."

38:13.219 --> 38:16.087
Lesson learned. Total disaster.

38:16.121 --> 38:18.089
No, honey. I don't think it was.

38:20.226 --> 38:22.767
If you're thinking about
adoption because things are tough,

38:22.768 --> 38:23.768
I can help.

38:24.063 --> 38:26.064
You don't have to do this alone.

38:26.098 --> 38:28.199
I will do whatever you want.

38:28.234 --> 38:31.970
Honestly, all I want right
now is just to go home.

38:32.004 --> 38:34.072
Please let me drive you.

38:37.243 --> 38:38.276
Say it.

38:38.310 --> 38:40.078
Say what?

38:40.112 --> 38:42.113
Say it.

38:42.147 --> 38:44.249
Okay, I admit it.

38:44.283 --> 38:47.051
Releasing the tape was wrong.

38:47.086 --> 38:48.920
And?

38:48.954 --> 38:51.356
And... you were right.

38:51.390 --> 38:55.193
- Thank you.
- Yeah.

38:55.227 --> 38:57.195
You don't need to play dirty.

38:57.229 --> 39:00.064
You never used pine tar or corked your bat.

39:00.099 --> 39:01.933
I know. It just pissed me off...

39:01.967 --> 39:05.270
those guys thinking they could
get away with attacking you.

39:05.304 --> 39:08.039
Well, if attacking me is all they got,

39:08.073 --> 39:09.340
then they got nothing.

39:09.375 --> 39:11.976
- Mmm.
- It just shows how scared they are of you.

39:12.011 --> 39:14.979
Sounds like Ivan is the one who
needs to be reined in, right?

39:17.216 --> 39:18.950
- Perhaps.
- Perhaps.

